description: Astral Witches is an NFT project with remarkable artwork with a rotational roadmap. Witches will be able to be a part of the CovenDAO which provides benefits and access to things such as expansions with brewing and something magical. Astral Witches will share 100% of their revenue from the secondary to their holders in the first season. Collection contains 4 different covens. These 4 different covens will compete with each other for the royalty share over the weekend. This income will be distributed to the holders on a weekly basis and distribution will not be equal for all Witches. There is 4 different covens for every witch and the coven with the most points by the weekend will get the most percentage of the royalty share. We will share details about how points will be collected. This is why we prefer a rotational roadmap and keeping the project alive with different contents. This will ensure that the volume is continuous and that new people are constantly involved in the project.
name: Astral Witches

description:
Soljaks are a collection of 6969 pixelated characters on the Solana Blockchain. 

Soljaks was founded on the idea that memes and laughter can bring communities together and bring people joy in a space that causes so much stress and has many highs and lows. We want to create a healthy community that not only supports each other when down and spreads joy throughout the crypto space. 

Community is very important to us and we want everybody feels like they can have a say in the direction that this project takes. Also, the art is CC0 - holders own the art so feel free to monetise it however you like.

The eventual discord server will be 100% gated to Soljaks holders.
